title: Pregnant Kim Kardashian Displays Baby Bump in Another Form-Fitting Dress
text: Kim Kardashian steps out in an all-white outfit to run some errands on Monday morning (October 12) in Los Angeles. The 34-year-old pregnant reality star put her baby bump on display in a form-fitting dress.
